contents:
[workspace]
members = [ "libmpv-sys",]

[package]
name = "libmpv2"
version = "4.1.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "kohsine <kevoh1516@gmail.com>",]
license = "LGPL-2.1"
build = "build.rs"
readme = "README.md"
description = "Libmpv abstraction that's easy to use and can play next to all codecs and containers"
repository = "https://github.com/kohsine/libmpv-rs"
keywords = [ "media", "playback", "mpv", "libmpv",]

[dev-dependencies]
crossbeam = "0.8.4"
sdl2 = "0.37.0"

[features]
default = [ "protocols", "render",]
protocols = []
render = []
build_libmpv = []

[dependencies.libmpv2-sys]
path = "libmpv-sys"
version = "4.0.0"

[package]
name = "libmpv2-sys"
version = "4.0.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "kohsine <kevoh1516@gmail.com>",]
license = "LGPL-2.1"
build = "build.rs"
description = "Libmpv bindings generated by bindgen"
repository = "https://github.com/kohsine/libmpv-rs"
keywords = [ "media", "playback", "mpv", "libmpv",]

[lib]
doctest = false
doc = false

[features]
use-bindgen = [ "bindgen",]

[build-dependencies.bindgen]
version = "0.69.4"
optional = true
